libibcommon
------------------------------------------
libibcommon provides common utility functions for the OFA diagnostic and
management tools.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.8.0-1
  libibcommon-devel-1.2.0-1bl4
  libibcommon1-1.2.0-1bl4
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-4
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-5.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-4
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://www.openfabrics.org/

Canonical download:
  https://www.openfabrics.org/downloads/management/libibcommon-1.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libibcommon-1.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libibcommon-1.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libibcommon-1.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libibcommon-1.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libibcommon1-1.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libibcommon-devel-1.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libibcommon)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libibcommon.README
  /usr/share/doc/libibcommon/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libibcommon/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libibcommon/ChangeLog

(libibcommon1)
  /usr/bin/cygibcommon-1.dll

(libibcommon-devel)
  /usr/include/infiniband/common.h
  /usr/lib/libibcommon.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libibcommon.pc

------------------

Port Notes:

